</ul>
<h1 id="operadores-loxicos" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#operadores-loxicos" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Operadores l칩xicos</h1>
<p>As decisi칩ns poden requirir m치is dunha comparaci칩n e se poden combinar con operadores l칩xicos para xerar un valor booleano.</p>
<h2 id="operadores-loxicos-e-valores-booleanos" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#operadores-loxicos-e-valores-booleanos" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Operadores l칩xicos e valores booleanos</h2>
<p>Hai operadores espec칤ficos que nos permiten conectar varias instruci칩ns booleanas. O resultado 칠 unha instruci칩n m치is complexa que en calquera caso se aval칤a como <code v-pre>true</code> ou <code v-pre>false</code>. Pode usar o seguinte conxunto de operadores para constru칤r estas comparaci칩ns m치is complexas:</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:left">S칤mbolo</th>
<th style="text-align:left">Descrici칩n</th>
<th style="text-align:left">Exemplo</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left"><code v-pre>&amp;&amp;</code></td>
<td style="text-align:left"><strong>AND l칩xico</strong>: compara d칰as expresi칩ns booleanas. Devolve true <em>s칩</em> si ambos lados son verdadeiros - true.</td>
<td style="text-align:left"><code v-pre>(5 &gt; 6) &amp;&amp; (5 &lt; 6 ) //One side is false, other is true. Returns false</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">`</td>
<td style="text-align:left"></td>
<td style="text-align:left">`</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left"><code v-pre>!</code></td>
<td style="text-align:left"><strong>NOT l칩xico</strong>: devolve o valor oposto dunha expresi칩n booleana.</td>
<td style="text-align:left"><code v-pre>!(5 &gt; 6) // 5 is not greater than 6, but &quot;!&quot; will return true</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2 id="condicions-e-decisions-con-operadores-loxicos" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#condicions-e-decisions-con-operadores-loxicos" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Condici칩ns e decisi칩ns con operadores l칩xicos</h2>
<p>Podes usar estes operadores complexos con ambas asignaci칩ns, pero tam칠n coas cl치usulas <code v-pre>if</code> e <code v-pre>else</code>.</p>
<h3 id="nas-asignacions" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#nas-asignacions" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Nas asignaci칩ns</h3>
<p>Como parte da asignaci칩n dun valor a unha variable, podes usar un operador OR (<code v-pre>||</code>).</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">let</span> isHoliday <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token keyword">let</span> isMember <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token keyword">let</span> hasDiscount <span class="token operator">=</span> isHoliday <span class="token operator">||</span> isMember<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Co c칩digo anterior, se expresa se un cliente pode ter un desconto ou non. S칩 칠 necesario que unha das variables, <code v-pre>isMember</code> ou <code v-pre>hasDiscount</code>, te침a un valor verdadeiro para que se asigne <code v-pre>true</code> 치 variable <code v-pre>hasDiscount</code>.</p>
<h3 id="en-if-else" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#en-if-else" aria-hidden="true">#</a> En <code v-pre>if...else</code></h3>
<p>Tam칠n podes usar este tipo de operador l칩xico nunha instrucci칩n <code v-pre>if/else</code>. No exemplo de c칩digo que segue, d치se unha situaci칩n na que hai dous port치tiles, un con desconto e outro vendido a prezo completo. Mediante o uso dun operador <code v-pre>||</code>, podes constru칤r unha cl치usula <code v-pre>if</code> de aspecto m치is complexo.</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">let</span> currentMoney<span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">800</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token keyword">let</span> laptopPrice <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">1000</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token keyword">let</span> laptopDiscountPrice <span class="token operator">=</span> laptopPrice <span class="token operator">-</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>laptopPrice <span class="token operator">*</span> <span class="token number">.20</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">//Laptop price at 20 percent off</span>

<span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>currentMoney <span class="token operator">>=</span> laptopPrice <span class="token operator">||</span> currentMoney <span class="token operator">>=</span> laptopDiscountPrice<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token comment">//Condition was true. Code in this block will run.</span>
    console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Getting a new laptop!"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
<span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token comment">//Condition was true. Code in this block will run.</span>
    console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Can't afford a new laptop, yet!"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>九勇 <em><strong>Suxesti칩n</strong></em>: Lembras que falamos sobre aprender a ler c칩digo? Que nos di o c칩digo? Vas poder obter un equipo port치til novo? Podes probar o c칩digo por exemplo en <a href="https://jsbin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JSBin<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> e ver o resultado.</p>
<h2 id="operador-de-negacion" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#operador-de-negacion" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Operador de negaci칩n</h2>
<p>Acabas de ver como se pode usar unha instrucci칩n <code v-pre>if...else</code> para crear l칩xica condicional. Todo o que vai a unha instrucci칩n <code v-pre>if</code> se debe avaliar como <code v-pre>true</code> ou <code v-pre>false</code>. Mediante o operador <code v-pre>!</code>, podes <em>negar</em> a expresi칩n. E ter칤as algo similar ao que segue:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">!</span>condition<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token comment">// runs if condition is false</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token comment">// runs if condition is true</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="expresions-ternarias" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#expresions-ternarias" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Expresi칩ns ternarias</h2>
<p>O uso de <code v-pre>if...else</code> non 칠 a 칰nica maneira de expresar a l칩xica de decisi칩n. Tam칠n podes usar algo chamado operador <em>ternario</em>. A sintaxe ten un aspecto similar ao seguinte:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">let</span> variable <span class="token operator">=</span> condition <span class="token operator">?</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token keyword">this</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token keyword">this</span> <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Este 칠 un exemplo m치is tanxible.</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">let</span> firstNumber <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">20</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token keyword">let</span> secondNumber <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">10</span>
<span class="token keyword">let</span> biggestNumber <span class="token operator">=</span> firstNumber <span class="token operator">></span> secondNumber <span class="token operator">?</span> firstNumber<span class="token operator">:</span> secondNumber<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>O c칩digo indica que, ou se lee como:</p>
<p><em>Si <code v-pre>firstNumber</code> 칠 maior que <code v-pre>secondNumber</code>, se asigna <code v-pre>firstNumber</code> a <code v-pre>biggestNumber</code>; do contrario, se asigna <code v-pre>secondNumber</code>.</em></p>
<p>九勇 <em><strong>Suxesti칩n</strong></em>: T칩mate un minuto para ler este c칩digo unhas veces. Comprendes como funcionan estes operadores?</p>
<p>A expresi칩n ternaria 칠 unha forma compacta de escribir o seguinte c칩digo:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">let</span> biggestNumber<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>firstNumber <span class="token operator">></span> secondNumber<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  biggestNumber <span class="token operator">=</span> firstNumber<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">else</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  biggestNumber <span class="token operator">=</span> secondNumber<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>九勇 <em><strong>Suxesti칩n</strong></em>: T칩mate un momento para reflexionar. Cal dos dous enfoques, expresi칩ns ternarias ou <code v-pre>if/else</code>, foi m치s f치cil de entender?</p>
<h1 id="proba-con-if-else" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#proba-con-if-else" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Proba con: If...else</h1>
<p>Para completar este m칩dulo, podes seguir a lecci칩n en <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/es-es/learn/modules/web-development-101-variables/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft Learn<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>. Desde a칤 podes activar un espazo illado en Azure para completar o exercicio. Un <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/learn/support/faq?pivots=sandbox" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">espazo illado<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> d치che acceso a recursos gratu칤tos. A subscrici칩n persoal non se che cobrar치. O espazo illado s칩 se pode usar para realizar os cursos de Microsoft Learn.</p>
